```plantuml
@startuml
actor 顧客
participant ":入力画面" as input
participant ":貸出コントローラ" as controller

顧客 -> input : 1 データ入力
activate input

opt [ログイン成功]
    input -> controller : 10 通常貸出()
    activate controller
    controller --> input : 11 貸出明細情報()
    deactivate controller
end

deactivate input
@enduml
```